blocks.content: Substitution for a six-place predicate. (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 4-Oct-2013.) (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 3-May-2015.)

thm br6(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3, setvar s4, setvar s5, setvar s6, setvar s7, setvar s8, class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3, class c4, class c5, class c6, class c7, class c8, class c9, class c10, wff w0, wff w1, wff w2, wff w3, wff w4, wff w5, wff w6) {
  |- wi(w3a(wcel(c0, c1), w3a(wcel(c2, c3), wcel(c4, c3), wcel(c5, c3)), w3a(wcel(c6, c3), wcel(c7, c3), wcel(c8, c3))), wb(wbr(cop(c2, cop(c4, c5)), c9, cop(c6, cop(c7, c8))), w0))
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s0), c2), wb(w1, w2))
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s1), c4), wb(w2, w3))
